room_title: Escape room "The Dorm" by Escape Matthews in Charlotte
room_address: 211 W. Matthews St. Suite 101, Matthews, NC 28105
room_description: Justin can’t locate his final paper and he has to turn it in to the professor within the next 60 minutes or he won’t graduate. He’s recruited his buddies to help search through his dorm room for his paper and get it to the professor’s office by 5 pm sharp!
